A woman is as much a force of nature as wind, lightning, and electricity.

She can destroy with one look or a flick of her eyelashes, she beckons because she is unattainable, and she can play with you by her own rules...

She enjoys life frantically, passionately, and gives herself to it with all her body and soul.
